							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/request/{{tx_hash}}/accepted",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"request",
								"{{tx_hash}}",
								"accepted"
							]
						},
						"description": "Updates request state to 'accepted'. This triggers:\n1. Agent restart with tenant configuration\n2. Retrieval of all UEs\n3. TAC restriction updates for non-tenant UEs\n4. Final state set to 'Completed' if successful\n\nUse the txHash from the Create Request response."
